<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="definite-adj">definite <strong><em>adj</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'defɪnət/    美 /'defɪnət/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-clear">1.★ <strong>明确的；清楚的 (clear)；肯定的；一定的：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>a definite answer
明确的答复</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>It’s definite that he’ll come. 
他肯定要来。</p></div></div>